metadata.name: Red hair girl
metadata.description:
For a slightly more normal person, even if the metaphysical repair is not uncommon, under this situation would not dare to move forward. But Xiao Che is not even hesitation, directly toward the group of abnormal white shadow.



As he came nearer, he suddenly realized that it was a man! A man lying there quietly!



"Who are you? In the vague see this was a person, Xiao Che stopped there, testing the sound.



The sight of the figure is no response, a trace of movement and no breath.



Did he pass out? Or... Dead?
